title: Truth or Dare • EP205
itunes:title: Truth or Dare • EP205
description:
Wilmington has a hidden little gem that Hilarie, Sophia, and Joy are letting you in on. If you have a fear of snakes... Beware!

 

Bad Boys Bad Boys... Whatcha gonna do? The Drama Queens discuss the evolution of the "cute bad boy" over the years. Are bad boys worth the pain or avoid at all costs?

 

Truth or Dare? Which do you choose? Felix was in for a real surprise and we dare to discuss it! When in doubt, stick with your girls.

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
